To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private ThreeBlackCrows _threeblackcrows;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_threeblackcrows = ThreeBlackCrows(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_threeblackcrows.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "threeblackcrows", _threeblackcrows.Current.Value);
}
